1
00:01:42,977 --> 00:01:45,477
- INUYASHA'S SWORD,
THE TETSUSAIGA,

2
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:49,477
WAS GIVEN TO HIM IN ORDER
TO SUPPRESS HIS DEMONIC NATURE.

3
00:01:49,510 --> 00:01:50,677
UNLESS HE MASTERS HIS WEAPON,

4
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:54,577
INUYASHA WILL ONCE AGAIN BECOME
A SLAVE TO THE DEMON INSIDE.

5
00:01:54,610 --> 00:01:57,177
UNABLE TO BEAR IT ANY LONGER,

6
00:01:57,210 --> 00:01:58,777
INUYASHA SEEKS TOTOSAI'S COUNSEL

7
00:01:58,810 --> 00:02:01,644
FOR A WAY TO MAKE THE TETSUSAIGA
LIGHTER TO WIELD.

8
00:02:01,677 --> 00:02:03,844
THE ANSWER LAY
IN DEFEATING RYUKOTSUSEI,

9
00:02:03,877 --> 00:02:09,010
THE DEMON WHO HAD BEEN PUT
UNDER SEAL BY INUYASHA'S FATHER.

10
00:02:09,044 --> 00:02:10,144
- UNH!

11
00:02:10,177 --> 00:02:11,610
AAH!

12
00:02:11,644 --> 00:02:13,544
AH!

13
00:02:14,110 --> 00:02:15,977
[GROANING]

14
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:19,344
- THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY TO STOP
THE REAWAKENED RYUKOTSUSEI.

15
00:02:19,377 --> 00:02:23,577
HE MUST USE THE BAKURUYUHA,
OR BACKLASH WAVE.

16
00:02:23,610 --> 00:02:24,610
- BACKLASH WAVE?

17
00:02:24,644 --> 00:02:27,944
- A POWERFUL ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE
OF THE TETSUSAIGA.

18
00:02:27,977 --> 00:02:28,944
- IT IS?

19
00:02:28,977 --> 00:02:31,410
BUT INUYASHA CAN'T EVEN
HOLD UP THE TETSUSAIGA,

20
00:02:31,444 --> 00:02:33,877
LET ALONE USE THE WINDSCAR.

21
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:37,244
HE CAN'T MASTER A NEW TECHNIQUE.

22
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:57,044
- HUH, I SEE
YOU'RE STILL HANGING ON.

23
00:02:57,077 --> 00:02:59,444
I'LL END YOUR MISERY.

24
00:02:59,477 --> 00:03:01,977
[LAUGHS]

25
00:03:04,344 --> 00:03:06,910
[HEARTBEAT]

26
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:14,277
[WIND BLOWS]

27
00:03:14,477 --> 00:03:18,377
- INUYASHA'S BECOME SEPARATED
FROM THE TETSUSAIGA!

28
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:21,744
- INUYASHA, PLEASE WAKE UP!

29
00:03:22,410 --> 00:03:24,677
INUYASHA!

30
00:03:27,144 --> 00:03:29,677
- KAGOME.

31
00:03:30,344 --> 00:03:32,177
[HEARTBEAT]

32
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:33,244
- HUH?

33
00:03:33,277 --> 00:03:37,910
THE AURA THAT SURROUNDS HIM
IS ENTIRELY TRANSFORMED.

34
00:03:43,377 --> 00:03:45,944
- [GROWLING]

35
00:03:47,610 --> 00:03:51,344
- HA HA! HIS DEMON'S BLOOD
HAS AWAKENED.

36
00:03:51,377 --> 00:03:52,177
SO BE IT.

37
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:55,277
THIS SHALL PROVE ENTERTAINING.

38
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:56,677
- [GROWLING]

39
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:59,977
- OH, NO.
INUYASHA'S ALREADY TRANSFORMED.

40
00:04:00,010 --> 00:04:01,177
- INUYASHA!

41
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:03,777
- [GROWLING]

42
00:04:06,877 --> 00:04:08,210
- STOP, INUYASHA.

43
00:04:08,244 --> 00:04:09,944
YOU HAVE TO CHANGE BACK.

44
00:04:09,977 --> 00:04:12,644
- [GROWLS]

45
00:04:12,677 --> 00:04:14,044
- WHAT WILL YOU DO NOW?

46
00:04:14,077 --> 00:04:17,110
IF YOU BATTLE RYUKOTSUSEI
WITH THOSE CLAWS,

47
00:04:17,144 --> 00:04:20,177
YOU MAY COME OUT OF THIS ALIVE.

48
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:21,477
- YAH!

49
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:24,777
- YOU MAY BE THE VICTOR.

50
00:04:26,044 --> 00:04:30,244
BUT THE TETSUSAIGA WILL NOT
BECOME LIGHTER FOR YOU.

51
00:04:30,277 --> 00:04:31,644
- [LAUGHING]

52
00:04:31,677 --> 00:04:36,010
- DON'T BE SO SURE OF YOURSELF,
LITTLE MAN.

53
00:04:39,644 --> 00:04:41,710
[LAUGHING]

54
00:04:41,744 --> 00:04:43,710
HUH?

55
00:04:43,744 --> 00:04:45,677
- YAH!

56
00:04:55,077 --> 00:04:57,010
[LAUGHS]

57
00:04:57,044 --> 00:04:58,077
- AMAZING.

58
00:04:58,110 --> 00:05:01,010
- THAT DEMON'S HUGE,
BUT INUYASHA WENT RIGHT FOR HIM.

59
00:05:01,044 --> 00:05:03,477
- IS IT OVER? DID HE BEAT HIM?

60
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:05,610
- [SIGHS] LET'S RETREAT.

61
00:05:05,644 --> 00:05:07,477
- [GASPS] WHY WOULD WE LEAVE?

62
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:09,244
- I THINK IT'S OBVIOUS.

63
00:05:09,277 --> 00:05:13,677
INUYASHA HAS CHOSEN
TO FIGHT AS A DEMON.

64
00:05:13,710 --> 00:05:16,777
- SO YOU'LL JUST ABANDON HIM?
COME ON!

65
00:05:16,810 --> 00:05:18,010
- NO, HE'S RIGHT.

66
00:05:18,044 --> 00:05:19,877
I'M AFRAID IF WE STAY HERE,

67
00:05:19,910 --> 00:05:23,844
MASTER INUYASHA
MIGHT EVEN COME AFTER US.

68
00:05:23,877 --> 00:05:25,310
- YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

69
00:05:25,344 --> 00:05:26,910
- WHEN INUYASHA TRANSFORMED,

70
00:05:26,944 --> 00:05:29,010
HE LOST HIS SENSE
OF DISCRIMINATION.

71
00:05:29,044 --> 00:05:33,110
THERE'S NO GUARANTEE
YOU WOULDN'T BE HIS NEXT VICTIM.

72
00:05:33,144 --> 00:05:35,644
- [SIGHS]

73
00:05:35,677 --> 00:05:37,244
I AGREE.

74
00:05:37,277 --> 00:05:39,677
MYOGA, YOU'D BETTER ESCAPE.

75
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:40,610
- HUH?

76
00:05:40,644 --> 00:05:42,477
- LET ME DOWN, TOTOSAI.

77
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:44,344
I'M GONNA STAY RIGHT HERE.

78
00:05:44,377 --> 00:05:46,277
- NO, KAGOME. YOU MUSTN'T.

79
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:49,710
- DON'T. I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GONNA SAY.

80
00:05:49,744 --> 00:05:51,310
ALL OF YOU.

81
00:05:53,044 --> 00:05:54,144
BUT I CAN'T LEAVE HIM.

82
00:05:54,177 --> 00:05:58,744
I CAN'T ABANDON INUYASHA
WHEN HE'S BATTLING FOR HIS LIFE.

83
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,277
PLEASE, TOTOSAI.

84
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:06,044
YOU HAVE TO LET ME DOWN
RIGHT AWAY!

85
00:06:06,077 --> 00:06:08,444
- ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

86
00:06:08,477 --> 00:06:11,077
IF YOU'RE REALLY
THAT DETERMINED.

87
00:06:11,110 --> 00:06:14,277
- WAIT. INUYASHA SURE IS
ACTING STRANGE.

88
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,844
- [GASPS]

89
00:06:24,144 --> 00:06:26,877
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

90
00:06:37,144 --> 00:06:38,444
- INUYASHA.

91
00:06:38,477 --> 00:06:39,710
- MASTER INUYASHA!

92
00:06:39,744 --> 00:06:44,210
- HE'S TRANSFORMED,
YET HE'S TRYING TO
PICK UP THE TETSUSAIGA.

93
00:06:44,244 --> 00:06:47,644
- COULD IT BE AS KAGOME SAID?

94
00:06:48,977 --> 00:06:51,577
- [HEARTBEAT]

95
00:06:54,544 --> 00:06:55,744
- THERE IS NO DOUBT.

96
00:06:55,777 --> 00:06:58,744
HIS SOUL IS BATTLING
AGAINST THE DEMON BLOOD

97
00:06:58,777 --> 00:07:00,910
THAT RUSHES THROUGH HIS VEINS.

98
00:07:00,944 --> 00:07:03,977
- UNH.

99
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:07,144
- INUYASHA, YOU CAN DO IT!

100
00:07:11,477 --> 00:07:15,977
- IMPUDENCE! HOW DARE HE THINK
HE CAN CONQUER ME?

101
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:18,710
- [BREATHING HEAVILY]

102
00:07:18,744 --> 00:07:21,310
- PLAYTIME IS OVER.

103
00:07:23,244 --> 00:07:25,977
- [GASPS] LOOK OUT!

104
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:27,810
UNH!

105
00:07:32,877 --> 00:07:34,010
INUYASHA?

106
00:07:34,044 --> 00:07:35,744
- LOOK. WHAT'S THAT?

107
00:07:35,777 --> 00:07:37,244
- HUH?

108
00:07:40,777 --> 00:07:43,177
- HUH?

109
00:07:45,377 --> 00:07:47,144
- THE SHEATH OF TETSUSAIGA.

110
00:07:47,177 --> 00:07:48,477
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

111
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,610
- I DON'T KNOW.

112
00:07:49,644 --> 00:07:50,610
- A-HA!

113
00:07:50,644 --> 00:07:52,710
THE BARRIER OF THE SHEATH.

114
00:07:52,744 --> 00:07:53,910
- I REMEMBER NOW.

115
00:07:53,944 --> 00:07:58,144
HE USED IT ONCE BEFORE
AGAINST THE THUNDER BROTHERS.

116
00:08:05,410 --> 00:08:06,477
- PRECISELY.

117
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:10,010
HE USED THE SHEATH TO WITHSTAND
THE LIGHTNING ATTACKS.

118
00:08:10,044 --> 00:08:11,044
- IT SAVED HIM.

119
00:08:11,077 --> 00:08:14,244
THE BARRIER MADE BY THE SHEATH
PROTECTED INUYASHA.

120
00:08:14,277 --> 00:08:18,644
- YES, BUT THERE WILL
NOT BE A SECOND TIME.

121
00:08:18,677 --> 00:08:21,444
THE SHEATH WON'T HOLD.

122
00:08:21,477 --> 00:08:23,810
- YOU CANNOT STOP ME WITH THAT.

123
00:08:23,844 --> 00:08:25,610
NOW, PERISH!

124
00:08:25,644 --> 00:08:27,810
- [GASPS] WATCH OUT!

125
00:08:28,677 --> 00:08:30,744
- WIND TUNNEL!

126
00:08:33,310 --> 00:08:35,077
- MIROKU!

127
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:38,710
- IT'S TOO STRONG.

128
00:08:51,944 --> 00:08:53,210
- HE DIVERTED IT.

129
00:08:53,244 --> 00:08:55,244
- THAT WAS A CLOSE CALL.

130
00:08:55,277 --> 00:08:57,077
- [PANTING]

131
00:08:57,110 --> 00:08:57,944
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

132
00:08:57,977 --> 00:08:59,810
IT TOOK EVERY LAST OUNCE
OF MY STRENGTH

133
00:08:59,844 --> 00:09:02,077
JUST TO SLIGHTLY ALTER
THE PATH OF THAT BLAST.

134
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:06,744
- HOW CAN INUYASHA POSSIBLY HOPE
TO DEFEAT HIM ON HIS OWN?

135
00:09:10,310 --> 00:09:13,244
- UNH.

136
00:09:23,277 --> 00:09:26,777
- HIS DEMON AURA IS DISSIPATING.

137
00:09:26,810 --> 00:09:29,377
- [GROWLING]

138
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:39,777
- NOBODY DARES
TO STEP ON MY SWORD

139
00:09:39,810 --> 00:09:42,744
AND LIVES TO TELL ABOUT IT!

140
00:09:44,977 --> 00:09:49,777
RYUKOTSUSEI, MY TETSUSAIGA
IS GONNA TAKE YOU DOWN.

141
00:09:52,977 --> 00:09:54,410
UNH!

142
00:09:54,877 --> 00:09:56,677
- [LAUGHS]

143
00:09:56,710 --> 00:09:57,510
YOU'RE SO VERY WEAK.

144
00:09:57,544 --> 00:09:59,910
YOU CAN'T EVEN HOLD UP
THE SWORD.

145
00:09:59,944 --> 00:10:00,844
PITIFUL.

146
00:10:00,877 --> 00:10:02,477
- LAUGH WHILE YOU CAN,
BUT I HAVE MY REASONS

147
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:05,577
FOR NEEDING TO USE
THE TETSUSAIGA TO SLAY YOU.

148
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:07,010
- [CHUCKLES]

149
00:10:07,044 --> 00:10:09,310
THIS TIME I WON'T
HOLD BACK FOR YOUR SAKE.

150
00:10:09,344 --> 00:10:11,844
[LAUGHS]

151
00:10:14,644 --> 00:10:16,110
- HUH?

152
00:10:19,477 --> 00:10:21,810
[HEARTBEAT]

153
00:10:21,844 --> 00:10:24,644
- HUH? IT'S NOT MY IMAGINATION.

154
00:10:24,677 --> 00:10:27,177
THE TETSUSAIGA IS
GETTING LIGHTER.

155
00:10:31,244 --> 00:10:32,710
- HMM?

156
00:10:33,577 --> 00:10:36,110
- [GASPS]

157
00:10:40,244 --> 00:10:41,044
- UNH!

158
00:10:41,077 --> 00:10:43,410
- LOOK! INUYASHA CAN
HOLD THE SWORD UP!

159
00:10:43,444 --> 00:10:45,077
- I SEE THAT!

160
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:49,510
- NOW'S MY CHANCE TO PIERCE
THROUGH RYUKOTSUSEI'S HEART.

161
00:10:53,410 --> 00:10:55,010
AAH!

162
00:10:55,044 --> 00:10:56,844
- YOU FOOL.

163
00:10:56,877 --> 00:10:58,677
HUH?

164
00:10:58,710 --> 00:10:59,710
- GRR!

165
00:10:59,744 --> 00:11:01,344
AAH!

166
00:11:01,944 --> 00:11:03,910
- [SCREAMS]

167
00:11:03,944 --> 00:11:06,510
- [GASPING]

168
00:11:10,377 --> 00:11:13,010
- [RASPY BREATH]

169
00:11:15,210 --> 00:11:16,744
- I DID IT!

170
00:11:16,777 --> 00:11:19,944
- HE PIERCED
RYUKOTSUSEI'S HEART.

171
00:11:21,177 --> 00:11:22,944
- IS HE DEAD?

172
00:11:23,544 --> 00:11:25,377
- UNH!

173
00:11:25,410 --> 00:11:26,844
UH!

174
00:11:32,444 --> 00:11:33,410
- SO LIGHT.

175
00:11:33,444 --> 00:11:34,710
IT USED TO BE SO HEAVY,

176
00:11:34,744 --> 00:11:38,044
BUT NOW IT FEELS LIKE
AN EXTENSION OF MY HAND.

177
00:11:38,077 --> 00:11:43,110
- HOW DARE HE WIELD
HIS SWORD AGAINST ME.

178
00:11:43,144 --> 00:11:46,110
YOU'LL PAY, LITTLE MAN!

179
00:11:53,010 --> 00:11:57,044
- HASN'T THAT UGLY THING
KEELED OVER YET?

180
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:03,077
- WHAT A DEMON!

181
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:03,844
STABBED IN THE HEART,

182
00:12:03,877 --> 00:12:05,177
AND HE ACTS
LIKE NOTHING HAPPENED.

183
00:12:05,210 --> 00:12:09,877
- RYUKOTSUSEI WAS A HANDFUL
EVEN FOR INUYASHA'S FATHER,
REMEMBER?

184
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:13,777
HE WON'T DIE UNLESS
HE'S HACKED INTO PIECES.

185
00:12:13,810 --> 00:12:15,744
- OH, NO!

186
00:12:26,244 --> 00:12:28,910
- NOW IT'S MY TURN!

187
00:12:29,544 --> 00:12:30,544
UNH!

188
00:12:30,577 --> 00:12:32,310
AAH!

189
00:12:33,777 --> 00:12:35,844
- [LAUGHING]

190
00:12:35,877 --> 00:12:39,710
- DAMN! HIS BODY'S HARD AS ROCK.

191
00:12:42,410 --> 00:12:44,710
- I WARNED YOU ONCE BEFORE.

192
00:12:44,744 --> 00:12:47,710
THAT TOY SWORD IS USELESS.

193
00:12:49,610 --> 00:12:51,677
- HUH? WHAT'S GOING ON?

194
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:54,210
THE SCENT OF THE WINDSCAR.

195
00:12:58,010 --> 00:13:02,710
THE WINDSCAR IS TWISTING
AROUND THE TETSUSAIGA.

196
00:13:05,410 --> 00:13:06,410
HUH?

197
00:13:06,444 --> 00:13:09,344
- YOU'RE THROUGH, LITTLE MAN.

198
00:13:09,377 --> 00:13:10,244
- HUH!

199
00:13:10,277 --> 00:13:11,944
RYUKOTSUSEI, YOU'RE IN
FOR A BIG SURPRISE,

200
00:13:11,977 --> 00:13:15,177
BECAUSE THINGS ARE
GONNA BE DIFFERENT NOW.

201
00:13:16,277 --> 00:13:17,477
HUH!

202
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:20,044
WINDSCAR!

203
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:28,510
- [SCREAMING]

204
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:32,644
- LOOK. THE WINDSCAR.

205
00:13:32,677 --> 00:13:33,810
- AMAZING.

206
00:13:33,844 --> 00:13:34,877
- INUYASHA!

207
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:36,777
- DID HE BEAT HIM?

208
00:13:49,844 --> 00:13:50,977
- NOT ONLY DID IT GET LIGHTER,

209
00:13:51,010 --> 00:13:55,310
BUT NOW I CAN INVOKE
THE WINDSCAR ANYTIME I WANT.

210
00:13:58,044 --> 00:14:01,644
DID YOU SEE THIS, TOTOSAI?
I WASTED THAT DEMON.

211
00:14:01,677 --> 00:14:04,377
- WELL, I'LL GIVE YOU
THE CREDIT YOU DESERVE,

212
00:14:04,410 --> 00:14:07,977
BUT IT'S TOO EARLY
TO REST ON YOUR LAURELS.

213
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:09,177
- HUH?

214
00:14:09,210 --> 00:14:10,510
- HUH?

215
00:14:10,544 --> 00:14:13,077
[RUMBLING]

216
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:17,744
- HUH?

217
00:14:27,577 --> 00:14:30,310
- IS THAT YOUR BEST?

218
00:14:30,344 --> 00:14:33,344
YOU DISAPPOINT ME.

219
00:14:33,377 --> 00:14:34,444
- HUH?

220
00:14:34,477 --> 00:14:37,910
- DID YOU THINK THAT DISMAL
ATTEMPT WOULD DESTROY ME?

221
00:14:37,944 --> 00:14:39,177
- WHAT'S WITH HIM, ANYWAY?

222
00:14:39,210 --> 00:14:42,777
- HE WAS HIT WITH THE WINDSCAR,
AND IT DIDN'T AFFECT HIM AT ALL.

223
00:14:42,810 --> 00:14:45,744
- YUP. DON'T SAY
I DIDN'T WARN YOU.

224
00:14:45,777 --> 00:14:47,010
- I TOLD YOU,

225
00:14:47,044 --> 00:14:50,810
MY BODY IS MUCH HARDER
THAN ARMOR.

226
00:14:50,844 --> 00:14:53,910
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

227
00:14:55,077 --> 00:14:55,910
- UH-OH.

228
00:14:55,944 --> 00:14:58,110
INUYASHA, YOU BETTER
GET OUT OF THE WAY.

229
00:14:58,144 --> 00:14:59,510
HE'S SERIOUS!

230
00:14:59,544 --> 00:15:01,410
- SO AM I.

231
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,444
HUH?

232
00:15:05,810 --> 00:15:09,044
WHAT'S WITH THAT DEMONIC AURA?

233
00:15:09,077 --> 00:15:10,810
- DON'T JUST
STAND THERE TALKING!

234
00:15:10,844 --> 00:15:12,310
HURRY UP AND RUN!

235
00:15:12,344 --> 00:15:13,277
- NO CHANCE.

236
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:15,610
I'M CONFIDENT I CAN
FINISH HIM OFF THIS TIME.

237
00:15:15,644 --> 00:15:19,177
- JUST BE GLAD YOU CAN
WIELD THE TETSUSAIGA NOW.

238
00:15:19,210 --> 00:15:21,010
LEAVE WHILE YOU'RE AHEAD!

239
00:15:21,044 --> 00:15:21,877
- TOTOSAI'S RIGHT.

240
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,910
- YOU PEOPLE JUST
DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

241
00:15:23,944 --> 00:15:27,244
I'VE BEEN WAITING
FOR THIS MOMENT.

242
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:41,110
AND BESIDES,
IF I KILL THIS THING,

243
00:15:41,144 --> 00:15:44,410
I'LL SURPASS
MY OLD MAN IN POWER.

244
00:15:44,444 --> 00:15:45,877
UNH!

245
00:15:47,144 --> 00:15:47,944
- SPEAKING OF WHOM,

246
00:15:47,977 --> 00:15:50,577
WHY DON'T YOU GO
AND JOIN HIM IN HELL.

247
00:15:50,610 --> 00:15:51,444
- IT'S HUGE!

248
00:15:51,477 --> 00:15:53,344
- WE'LL ALL GET
CAUGHT UP IN THE BLAST.

249
00:15:53,377 --> 00:15:55,544
KIRARA, MOVE AWAY.

250
00:16:00,210 --> 00:16:03,177
- [YELLS]

251
00:16:05,577 --> 00:16:11,310
- HUH? I'VE NEVER SEEN SUCH
A HUGE BLAST OF DEMONIC ENERGY.

252
00:16:11,344 --> 00:16:13,044
- GET OUT OF THERE!

253
00:16:13,077 --> 00:16:14,710
- THE FOOL!

254
00:16:15,444 --> 00:16:18,810
IN ORDER TO DESTROY
RYUKOTSUSEI'S ROCK-HARD BODY,

255
00:16:18,844 --> 00:16:22,044
