THE BACKLASH WAVE.

256
00:16:22,077 --> 00:16:24,177
HE DOESN'T STAND A CHANCE.

257
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:26,277
- I CAN'T AVOID IT!

258
00:16:26,310 --> 00:16:28,044
- [LAUGHING]

259
00:16:28,077 --> 00:16:29,844
YOU CANNOT ESCAPE ME NOW.

260
00:16:29,877 --> 00:16:31,477
- THAT LEAVES ONE CHOICE.

261
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:34,677
I'VE GOT TO CUT THROUGH IT!

262
00:16:35,844 --> 00:16:38,710
AAH!

263
00:16:51,017 --> 00:16:56,084
- I'VE NEVER SEEN SUCH
A HUGE BLAST OF DEMONIC ENERGY.

264
00:16:56,751 --> 00:16:58,484
- [LAUGHING]

265
00:16:58,517 --> 00:17:00,284
YOU CANNOT ESCAPE ME NOW.

266
00:17:00,317 --> 00:17:01,917
- THAT LEAVES ONE CHOICE.

267
00:17:01,951 --> 00:17:05,184
I'VE GOTTA CUT THROUGH IT.

268
00:17:05,217 --> 00:17:08,084
AAH!

269
00:17:14,251 --> 00:17:15,984
- LOOK! WHAT IS THAT?

270
00:17:16,017 --> 00:17:17,851
- HMM? IT CAN'T BE.

271
00:17:17,884 --> 00:17:19,284
- [GASPS]

272
00:17:19,317 --> 00:17:23,617
- INCREDIBLE.
THAT'S THE BACKLASH WAVE.

273
00:17:25,217 --> 00:17:26,417
- I SEE IT.

274
00:17:26,451 --> 00:17:30,384
I NEED TO CUT THROUGH
THAT SMOLDERING SPOT
WITH THE WINDSCAR.

275
00:17:32,917 --> 00:17:36,351
RIGHT ABOUT HERE!

276
00:17:43,551 --> 00:17:44,517
- WHAT?

277
00:17:44,551 --> 00:17:48,051
HIS SWORD HAS TAKEN CONTROL
OF MY ENERGY BLAST.

278
00:18:00,117 --> 00:18:01,651
IMPOSSIBLE!

279
00:18:01,684 --> 00:18:03,951
THIS CANNOT BE!

280
00:18:11,917 --> 00:18:12,751
- AHH!

281
00:18:12,784 --> 00:18:14,751
- THE WHIRLPOOL
AT THE TETSUSAIGA'S AURA

282
00:18:14,784 --> 00:18:18,317
IS PUSHING BACK
RYUKOTSUSEI'S ENERGY BLAST.

283
00:18:27,551 --> 00:18:30,151
- THIS CAN'T BE!

284
00:18:30,184 --> 00:18:31,784
AAH!

285
00:18:34,651 --> 00:18:35,784
AAH! MY BODY!

286
00:18:35,817 --> 00:18:39,984
HE SLASHED MY INVINCIBLE,
ROCK-HARD BODY!

287
00:18:59,817 --> 00:19:02,284
- WHAT HAPPENED?

288
00:19:02,317 --> 00:19:06,284
THAT WAS TOTALLY DIFFERENT
FROM THE OTHER WINDSCARS.

289
00:19:08,284 --> 00:19:09,417
- INUYASHA!

290
00:19:09,451 --> 00:19:10,584
- HUH? KAGOME.

291
00:19:10,617 --> 00:19:13,084
- INUYASHA!

292
00:19:13,117 --> 00:19:14,084
YOU DID IT!

293
00:19:14,117 --> 00:19:17,684
THERE'S HIDE NOR HAIR
LEFT OF THAT RYUKOTSUSEI!

294
00:19:17,717 --> 00:19:19,351
- OH! THAT WAS SO AWESOME!

295
00:19:19,384 --> 00:19:22,517
HOW IN THE WORLD
WERE YOU ABLE TO DO THAT?

296
00:19:22,551 --> 00:19:25,784
- UH, WHO, ME?

297
00:19:25,817 --> 00:19:28,051
- VERY IMPRESSIVE,
MASTER INUYASHA.

298
00:19:28,084 --> 00:19:32,284
I KNEW FROM THE START YOU HAD
THE STRENGTH TO DEFEAT HIM.

299
00:19:32,317 --> 00:19:35,951
- WE HAD TO PRACTICALLY
DRAG HIM BACK HERE.

300
00:19:35,984 --> 00:19:37,051
- HMM.

301
00:19:37,084 --> 00:19:39,617
- I UNDERSTAND NOW, TOTOSAI.

302
00:19:39,651 --> 00:19:40,951
- HMM?

303
00:19:40,984 --> 00:19:43,851
- YOU KNOW, YOU'RE MORE GENEROUS
THAN I GAVE YOU CREDIT FOR.

304
00:19:43,884 --> 00:19:45,217
[LAUGHS]

305
00:19:45,251 --> 00:19:47,717
WHAT DID YOU DO
TO THE TETSUSAIGA, ANYWAY?

306
00:19:47,751 --> 00:19:50,084
IT'S MUCH BETTER THAN BEFORE.

307
00:19:50,117 --> 00:19:51,351
- WAIT A MINUTE.

308
00:19:51,384 --> 00:19:54,951
YOU USED THE TECHNIQUE
WITHOUT REALIZING?

309
00:19:54,984 --> 00:19:55,817
- HUH?

310
00:19:55,851 --> 00:20:00,351
- THE TETSUSAIGA'S
ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE:

311
00:20:00,384 --> 00:20:01,584
THE BACKLASH WAVE.

312
00:20:01,617 --> 00:20:04,817
- THE BACKLASH WAVE? HUH?

313
00:20:04,851 --> 00:20:05,684
- HUH?

314
00:20:05,717 --> 00:20:07,551
YOU'RE SAYING THAT
WAS THE BACKLASH WAVE?

315
00:20:07,584 --> 00:20:10,651
- PRECISELY. LET ME EXPLAIN.

316
00:20:10,684 --> 00:20:12,951
IT USES THE ENEMY'S
BLAST OF DEMONIC ENERGY,

317
00:20:12,984 --> 00:20:16,584
ENSNARING IT WITH THE WINDSCAR
AND REVERSING THE FLOW.

318
00:20:16,617 --> 00:20:18,684
- SO IT ENSNARES
THE ENEMY'S ENERGY

319
00:20:18,717 --> 00:20:19,784
AND SENDS IT BACK AT THEM?

320
00:20:19,817 --> 00:20:22,751
- THE WINDSCAR
AND THE DEMON'S ENERGY BLAST

321
00:20:22,784 --> 00:20:24,584
BECOME LIKE WHIRLPOOLS.

322
00:20:24,617 --> 00:20:28,584
IN OTHER WORDS, THE ENEMY
IS SIMULTANEOUSLY BLASTED

323
00:20:28,617 --> 00:20:33,017
BY THE WINDSCAR
AND BY HIS OWN DEMONIC AURA.

324
00:20:33,051 --> 00:20:35,551
ANYWAY, THAT'S THE THEORY.

325
00:20:36,084 --> 00:20:36,917
- HUH?

326
00:20:36,951 --> 00:20:37,951
- THE TRICK IS HOW TO DISCERN

327
00:20:37,984 --> 00:20:40,651
PRECISELY WHERE TO CUT THROUGH
THE BLAST OF ENERGY,

328
00:20:40,684 --> 00:20:44,917
AND HIS AURA MUST BE
MUCH STRONGER THAN HIS ENEMY'S

329
00:20:44,951 --> 00:20:46,884
FOR THE TECHNIQUE TO SUCCEED.

330
00:20:46,917 --> 00:20:48,917
- I'M SO IMPRESSED, INUYASHA.

331
00:20:48,951 --> 00:20:50,551
- WHY? ALL I DID BACK THERE

332
00:20:50,584 --> 00:20:53,784
WAS USE MY INSTINCTS
AND FOLLOW MY NOSE.

333
00:20:53,817 --> 00:20:54,651
- HMM.

334
00:20:54,684 --> 00:20:56,184
HE'S SURPASSED MERE THEORY.

335
00:20:56,217 --> 00:20:59,884
PERHAPS HE'S DESTINED
FOR GREATER THINGS
THAN I IMAGINED.

336
00:20:59,917 --> 00:21:03,051
- INUYASHA, NOW IT APPEARS
IT WON'T BE SO HARD FOR YOU

337
00:21:03,084 --> 00:21:05,117
TO WIELD THE TETSUSAIGA
IN BATTLE.

338
00:21:05,151 --> 00:21:07,251
- IT'S EVEN BETTER THAN THAT.

339
00:21:07,284 --> 00:21:10,084
HA HA! WATCH THIS!

340
00:21:10,717 --> 00:21:12,684
HERE GOES NOTHING!

341
00:21:12,717 --> 00:21:14,317
AAH!

342
00:21:20,184 --> 00:21:22,317
- THE WINDSCAR.

343
00:21:22,351 --> 00:21:23,217
- WHAT DID I TELL YOU?

344
00:21:23,251 --> 00:21:26,984
I CAN INVOKE THE WINDSCAR
ANYTIME I WANT.

345
00:21:27,984 --> 00:21:29,417
UNH!

346
00:21:30,251 --> 00:21:31,784
AH!

347
00:21:33,617 --> 00:21:35,584
[LAUGHTER]

348
00:21:35,617 --> 00:21:37,817
- AAH! NO!

349
00:21:37,851 --> 00:21:39,551
- HEY, WE GET
YOUR POINT ALREADY.

350
00:21:39,584 --> 00:21:42,451
- THAT'S NOT THE KIND OF THING
YOU WANT TO BE FLINGING AROUND

351
00:21:42,484 --> 00:21:44,317
LIKE SOME KIND OF TOY.

352
00:21:44,351 --> 00:21:45,451
- HA HA!

353
00:21:45,484 --> 00:21:47,751
