355
00:21:50,251 --> 00:21:51,817
- INUYASHA.

356
00:21:51,851 --> 00:21:53,251
- HUH?

357
00:21:53,284 --> 00:21:54,451
- SIT, BOY.

358
00:21:54,484 --> 00:21:55,384
- UNH!

359
00:21:55,417 --> 00:21:58,584
- ONE VICTORY,
AND HE THINKS HE'S INVINCIBLE.

360
00:21:58,617 --> 00:22:01,051
- I'LL SAY. SUCH A SIMPLETON.

361
00:22:01,084 --> 00:22:03,217
- NOT TO MENTION A SHOW-OFF.

362
00:22:03,251 --> 00:22:04,951
- [GROANS]

363
00:22:04,984 --> 00:22:07,651
KAGOME HAD TO SAY IT.

364
00:22:09,917 --> 00:22:14,717
- WELL, HE'S STILL
A RUFFIAN, ALL RIGHT.

365
00:22:14,751 --> 00:22:15,817
LET'S GO.

366
00:22:30,684 --> 00:22:33,417
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

367
00:23:58,699 --> 00:24:01,999
- A GIRL NAMED SATSUKI
HOLDS A LONE VIGIL

368
00:24:02,033 --> 00:24:03,466
FOR HER WAR-BOUND BROTHER.

369
00:24:03,499 --> 00:24:06,733
SHE POSSESSES A FRAGMENT
OF THE SACRED JEWEL

370
00:24:06,766 --> 00:24:08,233
AND USES IT AS A CHARM.

371
00:24:08,266 --> 00:24:12,033
IF IT TURNS OUT TO BE REAL,
WE HAVE TO TAKE IT FROM HER.

372
00:24:12,066 --> 00:24:15,566
POOR SHIPPO.
HAS HE FALLEN FOR SATSUKI?

373
00:24:15,599 --> 00:24:17,799
BEFORE WE HAVE TIME
TO FIGURE IT OUT,

374
00:24:17,833 --> 00:24:19,033
A DEMON LAYS A CRUEL TRAP

375
00:24:19,066 --> 00:24:22,466
IN ORDER TO GET
THE FRAGMENT FROM HER.

376
00:24:22,499 --> 00:24:25,233
NEXT TIME...

377
00:24:25,266 --> 00:24:26,266
SEE YOU SOON.

